description:
Shuusuke is Nao`s big brother, and the eldest son of the Takanashi family.
He is currently in his 2nd year of high school, and loves collecting as many naughty magazines, DVDs and pictures that he can get his hands on. He also has a healthy interest in school swimsuits, knee-socks and striped panties. When he gets a glance of Nao`s panties his mind gets filled with naughty thoughts... even though he knows it`s his little sister.
name: Takanashi Shuusuke
